SAPI (Server API)
    echo PHP_SAPI 
        - or the same: echo php_sapi_name()
        - returns one of these strings:
            aolserver, 
            apache, 
            apache2filter, 
            apache2handler, 
            caudium, 
            cgi (until PHP 5.3), 
            cgi-fcgi, 
            cli, 
            cli-server, 
            continuity, 
            embed, 
            fpm-fcgi, 
            isapi, 
            litespeed, 
            milter, 
            nsapi, 
            phttpd, 
            pi3web, 
            roxen,
            srv (for HHVM),
            thttpd, 
            tux, 
            webjames
